nodes.body: btw, `import Mathlib` does not fix the issue; I'll see if I can spot what was missed.

@ericrbg I found it: I placed `fun_prop` on`ContinuousWithinAt.log` instead of `ContinuousOn.log`.

Note: I have already talked with Tomas and we *will* want to put the attribute on `ContinuousWithinAt` too, it's just been an oversight so far. I didn't do it for all the `ContinuousWithinAt` lemmas this time because they weren't already marked, and I wanted to keep review of this PR reasonable.
I had a quick look through the changes and it all looks good to me! Thanks for doing this!

Thanks :tada:
